The &quot;Paroubek&quot; budget took money from rents and health benefits
After the left, despite the government&#39;s opinion, added funds for farmers or officials, there may not be enough money in the budget for rents, sickness benefits or construction savings.
But neither for the interests of the state debt or international litigation.
This will hurt everyone who governs in the second half of next year, says Finance Minister Eduard Janota.
