Last year ČEZ allocated 18 billion to the budget.
Each year of the dividends ecological damages are settled, they serve to complete the account for the rents or they serve as a reserve for the prepared reform of the rents.
Furthermore, with this trick, according to EU rules, the true budget deficit increases to the level of 5.7% of GDP.
The money transfer carnival does not end here.
Almost three billion were obtained from the budget to grant various compensation to victims of communism and crime, or for litigation expenses, including construction savings.
It is not clear whether the state will need such funds.
It is a lottery.
If we lose any international litigation, we may have to pay for it, Janota says.
Afterwards, the Minister will have to save money within the spring or, in the worst case, draw on the reserve of the government budget.
There is also a hundred million missing for the Státní pokladna (State Bank) project, whose price is two billion and which has already been started. It should allow you to monitor online what the different authorities are spending on.
The first stage begins in January.
If the finance minister cannot find the money elsewhere, the project will have to stop and penalties will come, Janota warns.
