In addition, all employees on Saturday shifts will receive money for travel and food.
Because overtime work was the most urgent and problematic point of comments and complaints from unionists and strikers, who stopped manufacturing last week, management yesterday afternoon immediately decided to cancel all supplemental work for the month of December. Vaněk mentioned.
